General.Name: R3D Resources Ltd
General.Description: R3D Resources Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the exploration and development of mineral projects in Australia. The company explores for copper, zinc, gold, molybdenum, tin, and tungsten deposits. Its flagship project is the 100% owned Tartana copper and zinc project comprising four mining leases located in North Queensland. R3D Resources Limited is based in Sydney, Australia.
